descriptions:
Small dialog with height: 300px; width:800px;
Medium dialog with height:600px; width:800px;
Large dialog with height: 90vh; width:80vw;
 
Only for large dialog extensive data was incorporated, utilized width and height measurements in viewport units (vh and vw). 
This approach allows the dialogues to adapt dynamically to different screen resolutions, ensuring that the content remains easily accessible. 
 
Same approach should be implemented for the small and medium dialogs.
